#  Cafe Sales Data Analysis

##  Project Overview

This project was developed as part of my internship to analyze a Cafe Sales dataset using data analytics techniques. The objective is to transform raw sales data into meaningful insights through data cleaning, exploratory data analysis (EDA), dashboard creation, data storytelling, and statistical validation. The project helps identify customer purchasing behavior, sales trends, and business opportunities to support data-driven decision-making.

---

##  Objectives

- Clean and preprocess the raw cafe sales dataset.
- Perform Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) to discover trends and patterns.
- Create interactive dashboards for better visualization.
- Generate business insights using data storytelling.
- Validate findings using statistical analysis.
- Provide recommendations to improve sales and business performance.

---

##  Dataset

**Dataset Name:** Cleaned Cafe Sales Dataset

The dataset contains transactional information related to cafe sales, including product details, quantities sold, prices, payment methods, and sales dates.

