##  Project Workflow

### 1. Data Cleaning
- Removed duplicate records
- Handled missing values
- Corrected inconsistent data formats
- Converted data types
- Prepared the dataset for analysis

### 2. Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- Sales trend analysis
- Product-wise performance
- Category-wise revenue analysis
- Payment method distribution
- Customer purchasing patterns

### 3. Dashboard Creation
- Total Sales
- Revenue Analysis
- Product Performance
- Monthly Sales Trends
- Payment Method Distribution
- Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)

### 4. Data Storytelling
Business insights were presented using visualizations and dashboards to communicate findings effectively.

### 5. Statistical Validation
Hypothesis testing was performed to validate analytical findings and ensure data-driven conclusions.

